Malice/ Hellplague:

malice chuckles a bit and the trip concludes with no
problem.  He stops the group before the base
interance, and looked to Hellplague.

"Behave yourself please, I don't want to have to
wrestle you because you ticked the wrong bot off."

hellplague looked a little annoyed but nodded.

"Rodimus, we're back, we have Hellplague and her
friend with us."
